+
+/*
+ * This template is used for JavaScript code generation in element_hider_impl.cc
+ *
+ * Concatenated files from adblockpluscore
+ * (https://gitlab.com/eyeo/adblockplus/abc/adblockpluscore/-/tags/0.5.1):
